snippet.title: Solitary Echoes - Episode 1 released!
snippet.description:
We're extremely proud and to be honest also a little scared to announce that Episode 1 of Solitary Echoe's singleplayer campaign is finally released. Happy surviving!

Download: https://www.moddb.com/mods/solitary-echoes/downloads/solitaryechoesv1-1
